TO SET SHELL TO DEBUG WITH DDE (CONFLICTS WITH TOTALVIEW!):
MPI_FLAGS=edde
export MPI_FLAGS

TO UNSET SHELL FROM DEBUG:
MPI_FLAGS=f
export MPI_FLAGS

TO ENTER IN EACH DDE COMMAND LINE:
set  mpi_debug_cont=1
bre ntam
go

PARALLEL:
mpirun -np 1 <executablename> <inputfilename> <outputname>

PARALLEL WITH TOTALVIEW:
mpirun -np 2 -tv <executablename> <inputfilename> <outputname>
SEQUENTIELL WITH TOTALVIEW:
totalview  <executablename> -a <inputfilename> <outputname>



